column5: someone please remind me if 101 east out of Wawa over to Chapeau is paved or not. thanks.
Yes, it is, you're good to go!
thanks..... its either over to 129 and go north, which is way we went 3 yrs ago, or go north and across on 101.

If you've already been on 129 then you know why the first 100 kms or so are one of my favorite roads to drive! I'm only in a car though, I'm not sure I would want to drive that section while I was towing anything.
